text: Bronco Billy is a 1980 American western comedy movie directed by Clint Eastwood (who also stars) and also starring Sondra Locke, Geoffrey Lewis, Bill McKinney, Scatman Crothers, Dan Vadis, Doug McGrath, Woodrow Parfrey.
